it.csi.mddtools.guigen

Interface ContentPanel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    public interface ContentPanel
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Content Panel'. Il Content Panel rappresenta la singola schermata dell'applicativo. Può contenere pannelli strutturati con differenti tipi di layout.

    The following features are supported:

    • Panels
    • Name
    • App Data
    • On Refresh Command
    • Dialogs
    • States
    • Default State
    • Cp Commands
    See Also:
    GuigenPackage.getContentPanel()
